column5: ahh im so proud of u 🥺🥺
i have panic attacks almost nightly bc im afraid of waking up & feeling everything all over again, plus the dread of having to deal w every day shit in my life. it’s terrible
that’s awesome! i’m so proud. it’s the little thing that matter most when it comes to battling any mental illness. you got this :)
thank you. i hope it is too. it’s not going all that well so far
even when they claim to care, or when you think they may care, the reality is that after opening up to people, nobody reaches out to you or checks in on you to see how you’re doing.

this is exactly how i feel when i open up to people. in most cases, i start the convo surrounding my mental health, then i change my mind within 5 minutes and decide not to speak on it after all because i feel like more of a burden. plus i’m scared it’ll make people leave me
why’d this make me incredibly sad
I’ve been waiting.. for you to get your head out of your ass
It seems to be working out just fine for me
Too late, I’ve already started DEEing you
The only thing I’ll ride is you, but with your new “pre-marital sex is gay” mindset, that won’t be happening anytime soon
Nah, it’ll def be you. I mean, you are the only pussy here
Hi, I’m the ex. You know, my tactics were supposed to be kept a secret from him, but I see that is not the case anymore. Interested in trying out the M.A.C. system?
